name: kaonit_florae (engine)
description:
Cloudy smoke bursts in a purple ish off white manner from the 
string flow. The engine is a dense production mechanized form
of induction. It produces neonized masses of translucid non-existance
parts. All its funktions are non repetitive, each in its own way. This
is a frozen representation of a space-time moment of the workings inside
the systematic junction. All that it permeates and releases.
